{"sequence":79,"timestamp":"2026-04-15T14:58:14.178948792Z","event_type":"amendment_queued","details":{"amendment_id":"fr-4-52f93cb6","body":"finding_summary: `milestone plan` leaks the `__starting__:` reservation when setup fails before `draft_milestone()` runs, permanently wedging the milestone until `status.json` is edited by hand.\nseverity: high\naffected_files:\n- src/cli/milestone.rs:567-570\n- src/cli/milestone.rs:623-640\nremediation_hint: Once the reservation has been written, clear it on every subsequent error path (`EffectiveConfig::load`, `build_requirements_service`, and any other pre-run setup failure), or replace the marker with a lease/timeout-backed reservation so stale startup markers self-heal.","dedup_key":"63974ab760f8e53a070a27389c976d6450aca9c54b180b86cbf18e5110a677e8","reviewer_sources":[{"backend_family":"codex","model_id":"gpt-5.4-xhigh","reviewer_id":"reviewer-1"}],"run_id":"run-20260415130611","source":"workflow_stage","source_stage":"final_review"}}
{"sequence":80,"timestamp":"2026-04-15T14:58:14.187899211Z","event_type":"amendment_queued","details":{"amendment_id":"fr-4-d3f01aa9","body":"finding_summary: Once `pending_requirements_run_id` points at a missing or unusable requirements run, `milestone plan` has no recovery path and will repeat the same failure forever.\nseverity: medium\naffected_files:\n- src/cli/milestone.rs:154-188\n- src/cli/milestone.rs:190-221\n- src/cli/milestone.rs:553-565\n- src/cli/milestone.rs:678-695\nremediation_hint: Treat missing/invalid/nonterminal pending runs as stale state: clear the pointer (or allow an explicit restart path) before returning, and add a regression test for an interrupted milestone requirements run left in `drafting`.","dedup_key":"660b65a6f74d81cc763aedeeaf8095d7815dfff783aade718a0fb0d0ae8b77a2","reviewer_sources":[{"backend_family":"codex","model_id":"gpt-5.4-xhigh","reviewer_id":"reviewer-1"}],"run_id":"run-20260415130611","source":"workflow_stage","source_stage":"final_review"}}
{"sequence":81,"timestamp":"2026-04-15T14:58:14.196839581Z","event_type":"amendment_queued","details":{"amendment_id":"fr-4-8cc51e5b","body":"finding_summary: `milestone plan` starts a full milestone requirements run even when the milestone is already `running`, and only discovers the status conflict after the expensive planning pass finishes.\nseverity: medium\naffected_files:\n- src/cli/milestone.rs:145-152\n- src/cli/milestone.rs:553-573\n- src/cli/milestone.rs:618-640\n- src/contexts/milestone_record/service.rs:1377-1387\nremediation_hint: Reject `milestone plan` up front when the snapshot status is `running` (before reserving or invoking the requirements service), or at minimum clear the pending run when materialization is rejected for this reason.","dedup_key":"963ecd71ed66f6f9724460b3174c9e351c40f5165fccead280c8882a2bc19091","reviewer_sources":[{"backend_family":"codex","model_id":"gpt-5.4-xhigh","reviewer_id":"reviewer-1"}],"run_id":"run-20260415130611","source":"workflow_stage","source_stage":"final_review"}}
